        "\n",
        "### 🧮 Applying to Groundwater Equation:\n",
        "\n",
        "Starting with: $\\frac{d^2h}{dx^2} = \\frac{Q(x)}{T}$\n",
        "\n",
        "Substituting finite differences:\n",
        "$$\\frac{h_{i+1} - 2h_i + h_{i-1}}{(\\Delta x)^2} = \\frac{Q_i}{T}$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Rearranging for linear system:\n",
        "$$h_{i-1} - 2h_i + h_{i+1} = \\frac{Q_i (\\Delta x)^2}{T}$$"
